  <div class="callout-card callout-card--success">
    <strong>OpenSOAR is free and open-source.</strong> No license fees, no per-action pricing, no vendor lock-in. Deploy on your own infrastructure, own your playbooks and data, and contribute back to the community. Apache 2.0 licensed.
    <div style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
